Package: rvespa
Title: R Bindings for the Vespa VTK/CGAL Mesh Processing Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christophe", "Regouby", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "christophe.regouby@airbus.com")
Description: Provides R wrappers for all Vespa filters (isotropic remeshing, boolean operations, alpha wrapping, surface reconstruction, point set processing, and more) via direct Rcpp bindings to the Vespa C++/VTK library.
